                <h1>Mastering Background and Foreground in Visual Composition</h1>
                <p>The background and foreground are essential elements in visual art, design, and photography. The background provides context and depth, while the foreground highlights the subject and draws focus. Understanding how to balance these components can enhance storytelling and aesthetics, making images more engaging and meaningful.</p>
